<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Your Free Demo – Codespartans</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px;">
    <h2 style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-weight: 700; color: #111827;">Your free demo is ready!</h2>

    <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0;">Hi {{name}},</p>

    <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0;">
      Thank you for your interest in Codespartans for <strong>{{school_name}}</strong>.
      An admin will reach out to schedule your demo
    </p>

    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 24px 0;" />

    <p style="margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #9CA3AF;">
      If you did not request this demo, you can safely ignore this email.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
